body_html: There's probably some other installation of numpy that is interfering -- try searching for other installations, and if they are not needed, try removing them. IIRC, this is saying that tensorflow was compiled with 1.10.1 (likely) but the runtime is loading 1.9. Or maybe change the paths so that 1.10 is preferentially chosen over 1.9? I'm not an expert here :(
